# http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#object
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#object> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Identifies the object constituent of an issue when the issue concerns a particular assertion; this property designates object role rather than the overall issue target"@en .
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#object> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "object"@en .
