# http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#target
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#target> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Identifies the primary resource that an issue is about, such as a reviewed resource or an ontology/module addressed as a whole; assertion-level issues are instead designated through subject, predicate, and object"@en .
