<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Language concept"@en .
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageConcept> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Programming_language_concepts> .
# 
