<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageConceptApplicability> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Language concept applicability"@en .
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageConceptApplicability> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Programming_language_concepts> .
# 
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageSupportAssertion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "reified assertion that a language supports a language concept, optionally qualified"@en .
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageSupportAssertion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Language support assertion"@en .
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#LanguageSupportAssertion> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Programming_language_concepts> .
# 
